{"tid":1626134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超：若市民因為有病戴口罩，可以即場跟警員說，警員有合理懷疑，才可採取拘捕行動。","createTime":"2019-10-05T09:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:23:37.000Z","uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0ebac646ddb4f5ff023b9944106fece2068e6b","tid":1626134,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"李家超續指，就每一個情況，警方都是按實際事態及細節而行。若市民因為有病或宗教理由，可以即場跟警員說，警方任何執法行動都會根據法律。法律訂明，警員有合理懷疑，才可採取拘捕行動，所以市民如果有合理辯護的理由，可以即時提出，已可助警員明白實際情況。<br />\n<br />\npopo: 年輕人病咗戴口罩 = 有合理懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0d98f59149f82f63219e2333554893e655ed6f","tid":1626134,"uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"警員做埋醫生<br />\n可以判斷你是否有病<br />\n需要戴口罩"},{"pid":"db8e5abcb6f81c2110398d1322592a090e2ea47c","tid":1626134,"uid":54303,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4a0d98f59149f82f63219e2333554893e655ed6f","tid":1626134,"uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"警員做埋醫生<br />\n可以判斷你是否有病<br />\n需要戴口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:03:49.000Z","msg":"警察仲可以做埋法官添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51e15c7ff0b46962dc7e252791f4a1c9cacefc2","tid":1626134,"uid":4462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"db8e5abcb6f81c2110398d1322592a090e2ea47c","tid":1626134,"uid":54303,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4a0d98f59149f82f63219e2333554893e655ed6f","tid":1626134,"uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"警員做埋醫生<br />\n可以判斷你是否有病<br />\n需要戴口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:03:49.000Z","msg":"警察仲可以做埋法官添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"所以先加popo人工啫<img src=\"/ass